{"id":634456,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【立此存照】我很惨了-别逼我了-行行好-放过我/","date":"2020-02-06T09:06:13Z","modified":"2020-02-06T10:23:36Z","title":"【立此存照】“我很惨了 别逼我了 行行好 放过我”","content":"<p>2月6日，一名武汉推友 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monkeym4\">@monkeym4 </a>描述了自己因在“网上发布求助信息”遭到警察上门调查与人身威胁的经历，自己的亲人遭受了巨大的惊吓。该名推友以近乎哀求的语气希望警方不要再骚扰自己的家人。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634460\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"116\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎2.png 1196w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎2-300x63.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎2-1024x216.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎2-768x162.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎2-1080x228.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎3-4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634461\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎3-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎3-4.png 1198w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎3-4-300x247.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎3-4-1024x843.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎3-4-768x632.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎3-4-1080x889.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这名推友提到，自己的“父母都病了”，自己“说不定已经中病毒了”，老丈人接到了警方电话过于惊恐直接给了重病中的父亲电话，父亲“气都喘不过来”连忙来电“教育”，给了自己极大压力。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎4-2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634462\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎4-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"538\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎4-2.png 1194w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎4-2-300x293.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎4-2-1024x1002.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎4-2-768x751.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎4-2-1080x1056.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎4-2-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>该推友的历史消息似乎大部分已删除，从尚存的早期信息推测，警察上门的原因可能跟之前家属入院收治（不知是否确诊）网络求助，同时披露了当地医院的一些运行情况有关。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634459\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎.png 1198w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎-300x196.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎-1024x670.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎-768x503.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/武汉肺炎-1080x707.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>一些推友也回复提供了建议或支持：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>@New*****504：不能使用中国手机号注冊推特和F B，会被狗跟上。</p>\n<p>@Sa****h1：Send your tweets to someone else to post on your behalf.</p>\n<p>@o****a：小心。安你一個發燒的罪名，帶去跟病人一起隔離。台商就是知道接下來要大搜捕大隔離輕症患者，死都要擠上唯一回台的班機。</p>\n<p>@ls****7：我被国保打伤之后，一气之下把他的电话发到了网上，结果网友们连他参加的信鸽协会、连他住宅号码都人肉出来了，把丫给吓坏了。活该。</p>\n<p>@xu****023：你没做错，是他们错了。以后可能见不到你发推了～还是希望你父母能早日好起来。</p>\n<p>@de****nda：可悲啊，可悲，这个国家，真太可悲可笑了。</p>\n<p>@Ay*****836：We all know that ccp controls the internet. I am so sorry for you. Take care of your parents and take care of yourself. stay strong. Love from Germany.</p>\n<p>@aBI****W：唉，知道祖国的厉害了，祖国从不担心屁民的生命，倒是害怕外国，怕外国制裁，你如果不说，他们哪会拿鸡去看你们。哪会让你爸爸住院。</p>\n<p>@z14*****8：从来没什么恶魔降临，有的只是参与施暴的芸芸众生&#8230;&#8230;.</p>\n<p>@lo*****hk：你沒有錯！這是人的基本權利！</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案|<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\">武汉肺炎</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-632597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38912,39486,38923,39707],"tags":[39595,39752,9249,8604,13381,39750,39648,39747,14611,39611,22718]}